 our personalized demo.</p></div></section><section class=\"py-16 px-6 bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12\"><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-6\">What You&#x27;ll Get:</h2><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-1 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span><span>Tailored walk-through of SafetyLink platform</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-1 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span><span>Live Q&amp;A with OSHA-authorized experts</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-1 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span><span>Real platform features, not generic slides</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3 text-[#666]\"><span class=\"text-primary mt-1 flex-shrink-0\">✓</span><span>Bilingual (English &amp; Spanish) support</span></li></ul><div class=\"mt-8 p-6 bg-[#f9fafb] rounded-xl\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-navy mb-2\">Prefer Spanish? / ¿Prefiere español?</p><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm\">We can coordinate your consultation in Spanish. Visit the Spanish version of the site and complete the form there.</p></div><div class=\"mt-8 p-6 bg-primary/5 rounded-xl border border-primary/20\"><p class=\"text-[#666] text-sm\">This is a static marketing site. To request a demo or consultation, please email us directly.</p><a href=\"mailto:compliance@safetylink.ai\" class=\"text-primary font-semibold text-sm mt-2 inline-block\">compliance@safetylink.ai</a></div></div><div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-6\">Other Ways to Reach Us</h2><div class=\"space-y-6 text-[#666]\"><div><p class=\"text-sm text-[#686868] uppercase mb-1\">Call Us</p><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-lg\">888-373-7822</p><p class=\"font-bold text-navy text-lg\">833-780-0728</p><p class=\"text-xs text-[#686868] mt-1\">Monday – Friday, 8AM – 6PM EST</p></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-[#686868] uppercase mb-1\">Email Us</p><a href=\"mailto:compliance@safetylink.ai\" class=\"font-bold text-navy hover:text-primary transition-colors\">compliance@safetylink.ai</a><p class=\"text-xs text-[#686868] mt-1\">We&#x27;ll respond within 24 hours</p></div><div><p class=\"text-sm text-[#686868] uppercase mb-1\">Office</p><p class=\"font-bold text-navy\">Austin, TX 78701</p><p>111 Congress Ave, Suite 500</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><a class=\"inline-block bg-primary text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[#009c2f] shadow-[0_2px_6px_0_rgba(0,183,55,0.25)] transition-all \" href=\"mailto:compliance@safetylink.ai\">Email Us</a></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-navy text-white\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10\"><div><img src=\"/images/Logos-SafetyLink-1.png\" alt=\"SafetyLink\" class=\"h-8 w-auto mb-4\"/><p class=\"text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4\">The only legally defensible safety compliance platform backed by OSHA leadership and top labor law experts. Protecting workforces with bilingual training, audits, and compliance solutions.</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 italic\">SafetyLink is not affiliated with or endorsed by OSHA. Advisory support provided by former OSHA leadership.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\">Quick Links</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/solutions\">Solutions</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/services\">Services</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/contact\">Contact</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/en/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"https://app.safetylink.ai\">Login</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\">Compliance &amp; Trus